    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/7b8e1223e4424253a26ca5ad2b70fdf9.avif?t=1765309979\" width=1560 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Run to the Rhythm</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scuttle is a high-speed third-person platformer with rhythm game elements that blends music and momentum across vibrant, ocean-inspired worlds. In this genre-bending adventure, you play as a crab on a musical journey, gaining speed by hitting notes on beat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/c901ccddd70ff542e3c6c32be056d75c.poster.avif?t=1765309979\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/c901ccddd70ff542e3c6c32be056d75c.webm?t=1765309979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/c901ccddd70ff542e3c6c32be056d75c.mp4?t=1765309979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Charms</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect the blue musical charms to progress and trigger new sounds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/53fe9905de65db270fa7ea9fbf9bfb8a.poster.avif?t=1765309979\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/53fe9905de65db270fa7ea9fbf9bfb8a.webm?t=1765309979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/53fe9905de65db270fa7ea9fbf9bfb8a.mp4?t=1765309979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the Ocean</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race through unique beach-inspired biomes, from sunlit shores and open waters to volcanic coasts and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/e1896b85251ab459a21af2c6c3e9cbd3.poster.avif?t=1765309979\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/e1896b85251ab459a21af2c6c3e9cbd3.webm?t=1765309979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/e1896b85251ab459a21af2c6c3e9cbd3.mp4?t=1765309979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dodge Obstacles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evade urchins, lava, cliffs, and other hazards to maintain your speed and rhythm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/a004d4910ed776045f94ff83a5f54e23.poster.avif?t=1765309979\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/a004d4910ed776045f94ff83a5f54e23.webm?t=1765309979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/a004d4910ed776045f94ff83a5f54e23.mp4?t=1765309979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Platform On Beat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trigger platforming mechanics by jumping to the beat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/78de6b650b9c5c7376892ed048791750.poster.avif?t=1765309979\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/78de6b650b9c5c7376892ed048791750.webm?t=1765309979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/78de6b650b9c5c7376892ed048791750.mp4?t=1765309979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Run to the Beat of a Soulful Adventure!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the mystery behind this world and discover the true nature of flow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278200/extras/eb62dfa556465b0b89b0e57feaf95a03.avif?t=1765309979\" width=1560 height=611 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
